In large bowl, with mixer, beat sweetened condensed milk and water. Beat in pudding mix and cocoa powder. Fold in whipped cream. Cover and chill 15 minutes. Pipe or spoon a generous 1/3 cup of filling into center of each crepe. Roll up each crepe. Place on serving plate. Sprinkle with powdered sugar. Spoon fruit over crepes. Garnish with white chocolate curls (optional).